  "detailed_description": "Harry Is A Porter is an unusual adventure game heavily focused on car driving.<br><br><strong>Help Harry Find His Memory</strong><br>Harry wakes up with amnesia and becomes a freight driver for a fruit store. He tries to retrieve his memory from his daily life, but it is not a peaceful life that awaits him...<br><br><strong>Use Your Skills to Drive</strong><br>You need to complete the tasks arranged by Joe, the owner of the fruit store. Drive the truck to different places and collect the assigned goods. While completing different tasks, you need to solve various interesting puzzles.<br><br><strong>Game Features</strong><br>· Lovely painting style<br>· Incredible driving experience<br>· Explore different terrain<br>· Many strange trees<br>· Powerful bomb fruits<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064500/extras/be54b946fda26cca0fcaf7f5f05b686b.avif?t=1694796921\" width=160 height=240 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064500/extras/8d1b81e009daacd4117154ec72ff31df.avif?t=1694796921\" width=188 height=263 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064500/extras/be71b90b56d6b32b3710331459d8fb4b.avif?t=1694796921\" width=160 height=170 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064500/extras/58142ade0ffc1968e584b0699ca4c813.avif?t=1694796921\" width=175 height=275 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064500/extras/13a521df8b0ded15688f74d9a49790f3.avif?t=1694796921\" width=263 height=313 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"